org.eclipse.wst.jsdt.chromium.debug.core.model

Interface WorkspaceBridge.Factory

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    VProjectWorkspaceBridge.FactoryImpl
    Enclosing interface:
    WorkspaceBridge

    public static interface WorkspaceBridge.Factory
    A factory interface for WorkspaceBridge. It seems to tend to become a workspace relations type object, that is not tied to a particular DebugTargetImpl, but so far it only has 1 additional method.
